      <hedline>
        <hl1>How to Give Away $21.8 Billion</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Charleen Grassi letter on Jean Strouse's April 16 article praises Bill and Melinda Gates Foundation for donating $21.8 million to charity (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Thank you for a great article; I didn't know about the Bill and Melinda Gates Foundation (Jean Strouse, April 16). After reading it, I could care less about the antitrust violation.</p>
        <p>Charleen Grassi  Brooklyn</p>
      </block>
